        Thanks also to Jason Roma, Library   of Virginia, who modified the work of the South Carolina State Library for Virginia’s site. Artwork by Helen Correll is featured throughout DaybyDayVA.org and we thank her for her permission to use   her artwork and illustrations. </p>
